## ðŸ›  Troubleshooting

### **Record not found**
â†’ Wrong FormID or plugin name  
â†’ Plugin not loaded in SynthCALIOâ€™s load order  

### **No valid items found**
â†’ Outfit group was empty or incorrect  

### **NPC outfit unchanged**
â†’ Requires new game or using `recycleactor`  

